name: Cut Throat Crew (Movember special edition)
description:
MOVEMBER released special edition Tshirt! We're working alongside Movember this year to bring you this special edition T. All proceeds made from the sales of this will be given to the Movember charity. To find out more about the cause go to uk.movember.com - Black Tshirt - 100% cotton - Features soft front left chest and back print - Inside nape print - Sewn hemtag on bottom left - Wash inside out, do not tumble dry, do not iron over print S - 35/36" / M - 37/38" / L - 40/41" / XL - 42/43"

Order Information:

Orders placed before 2pm will be shipped out on the same day (Monday - Friday)

Tshirts and vests are all shipped out 1st class which takes 1-2 days for delivery. (United Kingdom orders only)

Hoodies, crewnecks, varsity jackets and polos shirts are shipped out 2nd class which takes 2-3 working days. (United Kingdom orders only)

Allow up to 14 days for delivery outside of the UK.
